<plot>"Tension &amp; Release" is a musical documentary about the Blues, a musical form that is rich in tradition and captured live at the International "Springing the Blues" Festival. "Tension &amp; Release" is a concert film that brings us the Blues as it is played by some of the most passionate and talented performers on the scene today. Their commitment to their calling is evident onstage and offstage, in this intense, insightful documentary.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?535530</url></doc>
